title: Multi-Genre Dubstep Journey - Special Ingredient B2B SAUMii @ Larimer Lounge by Special Ingredient
description:
Cooked up an extra special bass journey set with @saumiimusic for a sold out crowd at Larimer Lounge! Rinsed some of our favorite tracks we've shared over the years of DJing together.

Got some experimental wubs, some riddim march, some wave... a little bit of everything folks. Enjoy. We'll see you at the next one!

title: SAUMii
description:
SAUMii is a DJ and producer from Denver, Colorado, known for his genre-blending, high-energy sound that fuses experimental sounds, hip-hop, and bass music. 

With a passion for pushing boundaries, SAUMii brings an unforgettable experience to every performance. His dynamic mixes are a journey through diverse sounds, seamlessly combining heavy bass, unique rhythms, and experimental elements. SAUMii is making his name in the West playing venues such as Sunbar (Tempe), The Black Box, Larimer Lounge, Beacon, MockingBird, River Bar, and Your Mom's House. 

SAUMii is all about creating music that moves you, both physically and emotionally. Follow for fresh mixes, innovative beats, and squad of homies that push the limits of sound. 

Connect with me! 

Bookings/Collabs: Saumiimusic@gmail.com

PLEASE FOLLOW, LIKE, & REPOST!!
